OL,5, Shoplifting will be targeted like      
OL,6, organised crime as part of a plan to   
OL,7, help police to crack down on theft.    
OL,9,FA team of specialist analysts and      
OL,10,Fofficers is being put together to      
OL,11,Fgather intelligence on crime gangs     
OL,12,Fbehind much of the shoplifting across  
OL,13,FEngland and Wales.                     
OL,15,FRetailers have complained police are   
OL,16,Ffailing to tackle rising shoplifting.  
OL,18,FUnder the plan, police have committed  
OL,19,Fto attend more crime scenes and use    
OL,20,Ffacial recognition to target offenders.
